pages.home.hero.title: Download Freesm Launcher for
pages.home.hero.description: Freesm Launcher is a custom launcher for Minecraft that allows you to play with offline account without any restrictions.
pages.home.features.more-auth-servers.de: Use offline accounts without any restrictions, or Ely.by and other custom authentication servers to play Minecraft.
pages.home.features.customization.title: Customization
pages.home.features.customization.descri: Freesm Launcher has its own theme with catppuccin colors and Microsoft Fluent icons. It also allows you to set animated cat packs with background cropping support.
pages.home.features.prism.title: Prism-based
pages.home.features.prism.description: Freesm is based on Prism Launcher's code base, so you can expect it to have all features from Prism, such as modpack and instance management.
pages.home.features.other.title: Other Features
pages.home.features.other.description: Automatically copy in-game screenshots to your buffer history, show your current instance on Discord, play with Ely.by skins anywhere, and more!

pages.faq.issues.long-launch.title: My instance takes so long to launch
pages.faq.issues.long-launch.description: Try enabling or disabling your VPN or zapret. If it didn't work, try changing your Java vendor or version in settings.

pages.faq.issues.optifine.title: How to install OptiFine without launching the original Minecraft Launcher?
pages.faq.issues.skins.title: How to set your skin?
pages.faq.issues.microsoft-invalid-login: your microsoft account doesn't have a bought minecraft. you need to use an 'Offline' option in account settings

pages.faq.issues.no-languages.descriptio: Try enabling or disabling your VPN or zapret
